        <heading>Maintenance of militia units</heading>
        <content>
          <p>  ยง 47. Maintenance of militia units.  Unless the same shall be\nfurnished by the United States, the state shall provide adequate armory\naccommodations, bases, camps, target ranges, mooring and other\nfacilities and shall maintain the same for units of the army national\nguard, the air national guard, the organized naval reserve and the\norganized marine corps reserve allotted to the state under the laws of\nthe United States, accepted by the governor and organized under the\nauthority of this chapter.\n</p>
        </content>
